ce:section.ce:para:
The final structure of C-dots devices were.


Glass/ ITO/ZnO/C-dots/PTB7:PC71BM/MoO3/Al;



Glass/ ITO/AZO/C-dots/PTB7:PC71BM/MoO3/Al;



Glass/ ITO/AZO/C-dots/PTB7-Th:PC71BM/MoO3/Al.

Correspondingly, the reference devices were.


Glass/ITO/ZnO/PTB7:PC71BM/MoO3/Al;



Glass/ITO/AZO/PTB7:PC71BM/MoO3/Al;



Glass/ ITO/AZO/PTB7-Th:PC71BM/MoO3/Al.
